inputs: Create a modern, minimalist logo on a white background that is a line-art colored {subject_clr_0}. The thin line-art is a modern simple but stylish zig-zag shape that looks somewhat simmetrical, doesn't contain any small details and resembles a {shape} colored {subject_clr_1}. Under the logo there is an uppercase text '{text_1}' colored {text_clr_0}, using a {font} font. The overall design should feel sleek, tech-forward, and unique.

parameters.negative_prompt: no 3D effects, no photorealsism ,no shadows, no bevel, no gradients outside the shapes, no textures, no metallic effects, no photographs, no bends in the logo, no background patterns, no extra text, no glowing effects.
